"{\"uid\": \"thepinknews.com-2024-07-26-queer-aussie-surfer-going-for-gold-at-olympics-after-overcoming-chronic-illness\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tyler Wright is a two-time world champion in surfing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 53, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"score\": 0.999999946480331, \"rank\": 5.351960100292667e-08, \"text\": \"Tyler Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty)  Tyler Wright is a two-time world champion in surfing.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 75, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"score\": 0.999999946480331, \"rank\": 5.351960100292667e-08, \"text\": \"Tyler Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty)  Australian prosurferTyler Wright is a two-time world champion - but now she's going for gold at the Olympics\\u2026 although she will not be anywhere near Paris.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9989202899756319, \"rank\": 0.0010799815091547056, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 0.9999893168703635, \"rank\": 1.0675057900952569e-05, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}, {\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999986652938, \"rank\": 1.334705202499492e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will  beWright'sfirst Games - amid what she calls a \\\"sausage-fest\\\" in thesport.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a young girl becoming a woman in surfing, 12 years ago, it was an era of 'sex sells',\\\"she previously told The Sydney Morning Herald.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sex_in_advertising\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"sex sells\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sex_in_advertising\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sex_in_advertising\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sexy, straight, blonde, female\\\" surfers were most coveted and she did not fit into those stereotypes.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am built like an athlete, I am not straight, I do not have blonde hair.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While men were allowed to go out and be athletes - and get paid for doing it - a lot of women were not.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you invest in women, you will see them excel.\\\"\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While she's definitely going to the Olympics, she will be almost 10,000 miles from the French capital.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.763501255555004, \"rank\": 0.3095643091284881, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, she's headed to Tahiti, the South Pacific archipelago in French Polynesia which is hosting the surfing events.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999994405724665, \"rank\": 5.517312673178108e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9990542064593655, \"rank\": 0.0009466883510291748, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wright comes from a family of surfers, including brother Owen who won a bronze medal at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 0.9999893168703635, \"rank\": 1.0675057900952569e-05, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wright identifies as bisexual and met her future wife,Lili Baker, in 2021.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 0.9999893168703635, \"rank\": 1.0675057900952569e-05, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}, {\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"score\": 0.9999404605848029, \"rank\": 5.912776633673436e-05, \"text\": \"Baker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lily is just a vibe,\\\" Wright told The Sydney Morning Herald.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 0.9999893168703635, \"rank\": 1.0675057900952569e-05, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was working in a cafe in Newcastle [in New South Wales] when I was in town for a contest.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_upon_Tyne\", \"score\": 0.9606220350591493, \"rank\": 0.03882393056049353, \"text\": \"Newcastle\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_upon_Tyne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_upon_Tyne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so respected and appreciated [by her].\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, I asked her out, she said yes and here we are.\\\"\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair have \\\"an ease and openness\\\" coupled with \\\"love, respect and appreciation\\\".\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Tyler Wright (@tylerwright)  Wright suffered from chronic fatigue syndrome in 2018, telling the media that she thought she was \\\"gonna die\\\".\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"score\": 0.999999946480331, \"rank\": 5.351960100292667e-08, \"text\": \"Tyler Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Wright\"}, {\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 0.9999893168703635, \"rank\": 1.0675057900952569e-05, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She missed 14 months of surfing after winning world titles in 2016 and 2017.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has also suffered from a respiratory issue because of narrow airways that left her struggling to breathe during competitions.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She underwent a \\\"life-changing\\\" procedure to put \\\"seven screws\\\" in her head to improve her breathing.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through one of the specialists, we ended up finding that most of the time I am under-oxygenated and I am semi-suffocating all the time through my nose, and my airways are really small.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I should not be able to do what I do, according to my brain scans and my anatomy.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's really unusual that I am a professional surfer,\\\"Wright told The Guardian earlier this year.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"score\": 0.9999998648124893, \"rank\": 1.3512180452381252e-07, \"text\": \"The Guardian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel different going out and competing this season.\\\"\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also once spent three days in hospital, suffering debilitating period pain.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaseloginorregisterto comment on this story.\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The LGBTQ+ stories you do not want to miss, delivered to your inbox daily.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for registering!\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can update your email subscriptions at any time in theMy profilesection of your account.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articles  Latest News    What to buy now    Exclusive    Download the PinkNews app  Award winning LGBTQ+ journalism  About us  Editorial Policy  Contact us  Advertise  Work for us    Terms and conditions  Privacy policy\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 3041, \"entities\": []}]}"